Package: epa.gov
Title: EPA Envirofacts API Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the EPA Envirofacts Data Service API.
    Query TRI (toxic releases), facility registry, water permits, and greenhouse
    gas facilities. Auto-paginates large queries.
